      <section-body><paragraph-text type="body">Aspects related to the generation of ions (resp. plasma) should be classified in <class-ref scheme="cpc">H01J27/02</class-ref> (resp. <class-ref scheme="cpc">H05H1/24</class-ref>) and lower.</paragraph-text><paragraph-text type="body">For example, a microwave ion thruster with a peculiar acceleration grid should be classified in <class-ref scheme="cpc">H01J27/16</class-ref> and <class-ref scheme="cpc">F03H1/0043</class-ref>.</paragraph-text></section-body>
